text: "If I'm Lucky" is a 2017 song by American singer Jason Derulo and is a non- album single. It went to number 15 in Romania, number 18 in Lebanon, number 23 in Belgium, number 25 in Scotland, number 28 in the United Kingdom, number 29 in Spain and number 31 in Germany. == References == Category:2017 songs Category:Jason Derulo songs
title: If I'm Lucky (song)
